These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, musical
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, tennis
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| Sport     | tennis | rowing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding
1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Game    | mah-jongg      | billiard         |
| Sport   | skateboarding | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, musician
There 2 different types of food: orange, spinach
1. the videographer is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Job   | musician | videographer   |
| Food       | spinach  | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: french, indonesian
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, chess
1. the indonesian is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Nationality   | french  | indonesian |
| Hobby         | writing | chess    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, june
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, horror
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Birthday      | august | june |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | crime  |

